name: Mater lacrimarum
description:
Technique: Grafit on canvas
Original size: 20*40cm.
-----------------------
Hail to the Queen of rare 
delights Malefic and tragic 
Are the strings of her magic 
Screaming through the night 
She is sex and death and more 
The scent of evil in the glittering city 
A virgin and a whore 
For the horns of blasphemy
